someone suggested that we do Piñatas

00:01:12.330 --> 00:01:17.460
the idea of 50 of you with 50 bats did

00:01:17.460 --> 00:01:20.820
not seem to be a good idea so what we

00:01:20.820 --> 00:01:23.070
did we've actually looked into pull

00:01:23.070 --> 00:01:26.520
string Piñatas and the idea morphed into

